## ğŸš€ Common Tasks

### âœ… Test Firebase Connection
1. Go to **Status & Health** tab
2. Click **"Test"** button
3. Wait for result
4. Should show "Connected" with green checkmark

### ğŸ’¾ Backup Your Settings
1. Go to **Backup & Recovery** tab
2. Click **"Export Backup"**
3. Browser will download `appSettings-backup-[date].json`
4. Store safely (recommended: USB drive or cloud)

### ğŸ“¤ Restore from Backup
1. Go to **Backup & Recovery** tab
2. Click **"Import Backup"**
3. Select your saved JSON file
4. Click "Yes" to confirm restore
5. Page will refresh after restore

### ğŸ” Check Database Health
1. Go to **Status & Health** tab
2. View statistics (auto-loads on open)
3. Check all collections are listed
4. Verify connection status is "Connected"

### ğŸ†˜ Troubleshoot Problems
1. Go to **Help & Guide** tab
2. Find your problem in "Connection Issues"
3. Follow the steps provided
4. Use "AppSettings Not Found" if missing

