## âš ï¸ Important Notes

1. **Admin Only**: This feature is restricted to admins
2. **Non-Destructive**: Testing doesn't modify your data
3. **Safe Operations**: All actions have confirmation dialogs
4. **Real-Time**: Status updates are live
5. **Regular Backups**: Export backup regularly (weekly recommended)
6. **Documentation**: Visit Firebase docs for advanced topics

