---

## â“ FAQ

**Q: Can I delete collections from this page?**
A: No, this page is read-only for safety. Collections are managed through Firebase Console.

**Q: How often should I backup?**
A: Weekly is recommended, or before major changes.

**Q: What if connection test fails?**
A: Check your internet connection and see Help & Guide tab for troubleshooting.

**Q: Can non-admins access this?**
A: No, this is admin-only for security reasons.

**Q: Is my backup encrypted?**
A: It's a plain JSON file, so store backups securely.

**Q: Can I schedule automatic backups?**
A: Not yet, but manual export is quick and easy.

